  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare the safety and efficacy of ceftobiprole medocaril
      versus vancomycin plus aztreonam in the treatment of patients with acute bacterial skin and
      skin structure infections.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
